ery Good)</li>\n        <li><strong>4,000\u20135,999 TCS \u2192 3\u2605</strong> (Good)</li>\n        <li><strong>2,000\u20133,999 TCS \u2192 2\u2605</strong> (Caution)</li>\n        <li><strong>0\u20131,999 TCS \u2192 1\u2605</strong> (Avoid / High Risk)</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Tools & Resources -->\n    <h2 style=\"color:#ffcc33; font-size:1.75rem; margin:42px 0 12px;\">\n      Useful Tools for Comparing Ratings &amp; Understanding TCS\n    </h2>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr)); gap:20px;\">\n\n      <!-- Bonus Calculator Tool -->\n      <div style=\"background:#080826; border:1px solid #1c1c4a; border-radius:12px; padding:20px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#ffcc33; margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">\n          Casino Bonus Calculator\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.8;\">\n          Use our <strong>casino bonus calculator</strong> to estimate the real value of a welcome offer before you play.\n          Enter your deposit, match percentage and wagering requirements to understand how tough a bonus is to clear.\n          It\u2019s the same bonus maths we use inside the <strong>TopCasinoScout Score (TCS)</strong>.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"/bonus-calculator-tool\"\n           style=\"display:inline-block; margin-top:4px; padding:8px 14px; border-radius:999px; background:#ffcc33; color:#05051b; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none;\">\n          Open Bonus Calculator \u2192\n        </a>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- AI Bonus Finder -->\n      <div style=\"background:#080826; border:1px solid #1c1c4a; border-radius:12px; padding:20px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#ffcc33; margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">\n          AI Bonus Finder\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.8;\">\n          Our <strong>AI Bonus Finder</strong> helps players filter casinos by deposit size, bonus type, and region. It uses\n          the same <strong>TCS rating data</strong> to highlight safer, better-value welcome offers.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"/casino-bonus-finder/\"\n           style=\"display:inline-block; margin-top:4px; padding:8px 14px; border-radius:999px; background:#ffcc33; color:#05051b; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none;\">\n          Try AI Bonus Finder \u2192\n        </a>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Reviews & Rankings -->\n      <div style=\"background:#080826; border:1px solid #1c1c4a; border-radius:12px; padding:20px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"color:#ffcc33; margin:0 0 8px; font-size:1.1rem;\">\n          Detailed Casino Reviews &amp; Rankings\n        </h3>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0 0 12px; line-height:1.8;\">\n          Browse our <strong>online casino reviews</strong> sorted by <strong>TCS score</strong> or A\u2013Z. Each review shows a breakdown\n          across the same categories so you can compare casinos consistently.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"/detailed-casino-reviews/\"\n           style=\"display:inline-block; margin-top:4px; padding:8px 14px; border-radius:999px; background:#ffcc33; color:#05051b; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none;\">\n          View Casino Reviews &amp; Rankings \u2192\n        </a>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- FAQ Section Wrapper -->\n    <div style=\"background:#080826; border:1px solid #1c1c4a; border-radius:14px; padding:28px;\">\n      <h3 style=\"color:#ffcc33; font-size:1.4rem; margin:0 0 18px;\">\n        Frequently Asked Questions About Our Casino Ratings\n      </h3>\n\n      <!-- START FAQ ITEMS (All Matching Style) -->\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">Why is the TopCasinoScout scoring system different?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          Many casino sites use subjective opinions or paid rankings. TopCasinoScout applies a fixed, numeric \n          10,000-point model with transparent rules. Each casino is measured using the same criteria \u2014 payouts, \n          bonus terms, licensing strength, games, support, and independent player reviews \u2014 ensuring unbiased \n          and consistent comparisons.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">How do you ensure ratings remain fair and independent?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          We do not sell or accept payments for higher scores. Our team directly tests support responsiveness, \n          verifies licensing with regulators, calculates real bonus value, and reviews external player feedback. \n          Our full methodology is openly published in our \n          <a href=\"/casino-review-guidelines\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">Casino Review Guidelines</a>.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">What happens if a casino shows serious issues or red flags?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          Fake licensing, non-payment patterns, tampered games, or systematic unfair behaviour results in a \n          score of 0 / 10,000 and placement on our warning lists. Protecting players is our top priority.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">Do new casinos get an unfair disadvantage?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          No. If a casino has fewer than 50 verified reviews, Trustpilot scoring is marked as limited. The internal \n          7,500-point score is temporarily scaled to 10,000 so genuine new casinos are not penalised simply for \n          being new to the market.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">How often are casino scores updated?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          Scores are updated whenever a casino changes withdrawal speed, bonus terms, game catalogue, support \n          quality, licence status, or when new player complaints appear. Major issues trigger immediate review.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- NEW FAQ ITEMS (Consistent Style) -->\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">How do you verify whether a casino\u2019s licence is genuine?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          We cross-check licence details directly with the regulator\u2019s official database, confirming the operator name,\n          licence number, approved activities, and linked domains. Any inconsistencies or unverifiable claims lead to\n          significant score reductions \u2014 and clear cases of misrepresentation trigger automatic blacklisting.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">What makes a bonus high or low value in your scoring model?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          We analyse match percentage, bonus cap, wagering requirements, game contributions, max bet limits, and \n          transparency. High-value bonuses have low wagering, fair terms, and no hidden restrictions. Low-value \n          offers often include high wagering, confusing conditions, or max-cashout traps.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">Why do some casinos with large game libraries still score moderately?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          A big game count does not automatically mean quality. We look at the presence of top studios, fairness audits,\n          RNG certifications, and the strength of the live casino section. Casinos can offer thousands of games but still\n          lack reputable providers or trusted software, resulting in moderate scores.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">What types of player complaints affect scores the most?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          We monitor patterns, not isolated complaints. Repeated issues such as delayed withdrawals, unfair term changes,\n          unexplained account closures, or slow KYC directly impact Payments, Licensing, and Support scores. Proven \n          non-payment behaviour triggers immediate blacklisting.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">How does TopCasinoScout compare to other review sites?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          Many review sites rely on opinions or commercial incentives. We use a transparent 10,000-point checklist \n          that evaluates real metrics: bonus value, wagering fairness, payout timing, licensing verification, game \n          quality, support testing, and independent Trustpilot reviews. Our scores are numerical, repeatable, and \n          impossible to influence with payments.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:0;\">\n        <h4 style=\"color:#ffd86a; margin:0 0 8px;\">Where can I find help for responsible gambling?</h4>\n        <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; margin:0; line-height:1.7;\">\n          If you need support or guidance, visit our \n          <a href=\"/responsible-gambling\" style=\"color:#ffcc33; text-decoration:none;\">Responsible Gambling</a>\n          page. It includes helplines, tools, limits, time-outs, and resources for maintaining safe and controlled play.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- END FAQ ITEMS -->\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section style=\"background:#0e0833; padding:40px 20px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;\">\n\n    <h3 style=\"color:#ffcc33; font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:12px;\">\n      Questions About Our Rating System?\n    </h3>\n\n    <p style=\"color:#a8c7ff; line-height:1.7; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto 20px;\">\n      We continually refine and audit the TopCasinoScout Score (TCS) to ensure our casino ratings remain accurate,\n      transparent, and fair. If you have feedback about our scoring rules, want to report an update, or believe a casino\n      should be re-evaluated, our editorial team would like to hear from you.\n    </p>\n\n    <p style=\"color:#ffcc33; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:0;\">\n      Contact our rating team: \n      <a href=\"mailto:team@localhost\" style=\"color:#ffd86a; text-decoration:none;\">\n        team@localhost\n      </a>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>";
